docs {
  ## Create Stock In Detail (standalone)
  สร้างรายการย่อยของ stock-in ผ่าน standalone endpoint

  Creates a new stock-in detail record via the standalone stock-in-detail controller.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `inventory_management.stock_in:update`
  - **Roles**: Purchase

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "description": "Rice Jasmine 50kg bag",
    "qty": 10.5,
    "cost_per_unit": 1250.00,
    "total_cost": 13125.00,
    "note": "Received from supplier",
    "product_name": "Rice Jasmine",
    "product_local_name": "ข้าวหอมมะลิ",
    "location_code": "MAIN-01",
    "location_name": "Main Store",
    "product_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "location_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "info": null,
    "dimension": null
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 201,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | Invalid request body |
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `inventory_management.stock_in:update` permission |
}
